name: Geekbench: Object Remover
description: Removes an object (using a mask) from a 3MP photo, and fills in the gap left behind using the iterative PatchMatch Inpainting approach (Barnes et al. 2009).The score is calibrated against a baseline score of 2,500 (Dell Precision 3460 with a Core i7-12700 processor) as per the Geekbench 6 Benchmark Internals.
